channel.description: The latest CVEs for Jenkins project -- Jenkins Sounds Plugin

item.title: CVE-2020-2097|2024-08-04T06:54:00.613Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20sounds%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Sounds Plugin 0.5 and earlier does not perform permission checks in URLs performing form validation, allowing attackers with Overall/Read access to execute arbitrary OS commands as the OS user account running Jenkins.

item.title: CVE-2020-2098|2024-08-04T07:01:39.583Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20sounds%20plugin
item.description: A cross-site request forgery vulnerability in Jenkins Sounds Plugin 0.5 and earlier allows attacker to execute arbitrary OS commands as the OS user account running Jenkins.
